 You're interrupting my lecture, but you're cute.

00:18:09.080 --> 00:18:10.640
 So quit chewing on a pen.

00:18:10.640 --> 00:18:12.960
 Chew on your chew toys that I gave you, okay?

00:18:12.960 --> 00:18:15.160
 Let me get through this lecture.

00:18:15.160 --> 00:18:17.280
 Okay, you can get down.

00:18:17.280 --> 00:18:19.360
 Just quit chewing on a...

00:18:19.360 --> 00:18:20.920
 Sorry about that.

00:18:20.920 --> 00:18:23.440
 Dog introduction, dog interruption.

00:18:23.440 --> 00:18:24.920
 I was just hearing chewing noises

00:18:24.920 --> 00:18:26.560
 and I thought I took everything

00:18:26.560 --> 00:18:28.880
 but then there was one pen on the floor.

00:18:28.880 --> 00:18:32.800
 And so the pen, poor pen, meets Mr. Puppy.

